      "startOffset": 2839763,
      "endOffset": 2839806,
      "summary": "东方长凡与魔道蛊仙们交战"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_0805",
      "paragraphId": "ch_0805_p0046",
      "startOffset": 2840615,
      "endOffset": 2840664,
      "summary": "东方部族与小人族是盟友关系，小人族蛊仙方兄（小人蛊仙）将方寸山借给东方长凡使用。"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_0805",
      "paragraphId": "ch_0805_p0050",
      "startOffset": 2840759,
      "endOffset": 2840789,
      "summary": "东方长凡与魔道蛊仙（皮水寒、黑楼兰、残阳老君、自在书生等）正在战斗。"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_0805",
      "paragraphId": "ch_0805_p0067",
      "startOffset": 2841338,
      "endOffset": 2841388,
      "summary": "小人族蛊仙领导小人一族，和东方一族联盟，为本族求得生存空间。"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_0805",
      "paragraphId": "ch_0805_p0075",
      "startOffset": 2841625,
      "endOffset": 2841656,
      "summary": "众魔以自在书生为首，激战东方长凡、残阳老君和小人蛊仙。"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_0805",
      "paragraphId": "ch_0805_p0088",
      "startOffset": 2842120,
      "endOffset": 2842150,
      "summary": "方源趁众魔战斗时偷偷采集资源，引起众魔愤怒。"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_0805",
      "paragraphId": "ch_0805_p0031",
      "startOffset": 2840062,
      "endOffset": 2840089,
      "summary": "东方长凡返回碧潭福地，与魔道蛊仙们激战，并发动福地权限压制魔道蛊仙的凡道杀招"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_0805",
      "paragraphId": "ch_0805_p0005",
      "startOffset": 2839037,
      "endOffset": 2839064,
      "summary": "东方长凡与茅草屋失去联系"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_0805",
      "paragraphId": "ch_0805_p0016",
      "startOffset": 2839441,
      "endOffset": 2839486,
      "summary": "东方长凡催动杀招万星飞萤"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_0805",
      "paragraphId": "ch_0805_p0036",
      "startOffset": 2840269,
      "endOffset": 2840341,
      "summary": "东方长凡在碧潭福地战斗，魔道蛊仙攻势孱弱后，东方长凡俯冲到嫣然海禁地，看到花海桃林被毁，桃太狼群被斩杀。"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_0805",
      "paragraphId": "ch_0805_p0038",
      "startOffset": 2840377,
      "endOffset": 2840443,
      "summary": "东方长凡向小人蛊仙方兄求助，方兄回应并将方寸山交给东方余亮。"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_0805",
      "paragraphId": "ch_0805_p0056",
      "startOffset": 2840893,
      "endOffset": 2840918,
      "summary": "魔道蛊仙使用天花黯淡、千解、冰龙锁、力道巨手四大仙道杀招攻击东方长凡，残阳老君使用追命火迫使自在书生后退。"
    },
    {
      "sourcePath": "D:\\workspace\\CodeBuddyWorkSpace\\RebornG_codebuddy\\doc\\original work\\reverend-insanity.txt",
      "chapterId": "ch_0805",
      "paragraphId": "ch_0805_p0078",
      "startOffset": 2841705,
      "endOffset": 2841721,
      "summary": "自在书生使出千解对拼大而化小，但被后者所克。"
    }
